<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
  xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui">
  <ui:style>
  .text {
    font-family:arial, helvetica;
    font-size: 3em;
    text-align: justify;
  }
  .ov_table {
    border: 1px solid #A0A0A0;
    background-color: #E0E0E0;
    width: 90%;
    position: absolute;
    left: 5%;
    top: 2%;
    border-radius: 0.5em;
    padding: 10px;
  }
  .panel {
    background-color: #E0E0E0;
  }
  .scrollPanel {
    height: 100%;
  }
  </ui:style>
  
  <ui:with field='res' type='es.erni.demo.client.style.Styles.Resources' />
  
  <g:ScrollPanel styleName="{style.scrollPanel}">
  
  <g:HTMLPanel styleName="{style.panel}">
    
   <table class='{style.ov_table}'>
      <tr>
        <td class="{style.text}">
          <ul>
            <li>Java Project development using <a href="http://maven.apache.org" target="_blank">Apache Maven</a> and <a href="http://www.eclipse.org" target="_blank">Eclipse IDE</a>, <a href="http://ant.apache.org" target="_blank">Apache Ant</a></li>
            <li>Web applications development:</li>
              <ul>
                <li>Deep knowledge in Complex browser-based applications with <a href="http://code.google.com/webtoolkit/overview.html" target="_blank">Google Web Toolkit (GWT)</a></li>
                <li>Model-View-Presenter (MVP) and/or Model-View-Controller (MVC) architecture.</li>
                <li>External GWT libraries like <a href="http://www.sencha.com/products/extgwt/" target="_blank">Ext GWT</a></li>
                <li>Web Servers and Servlet Containers: <a href="http://tomcat.apache.org" target="_blank">Apache Tomcat</a>, <a href="http://jetty.codehaus.org/jetty/" target="_blank">Jetty Web Server</a> and <a href="http://httpd.apache.org/" target="_blank">Apache HTTP Server</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://struts.apache.org/" target="_blank">Apache Struts 1 and 2</a></li>
                <li>Java, JSP, PHP, XML, (X)HTML, CSS, Javascript</li>
              </ul>
            <li>Web Services development skills:</li>
              <ul>
                <li><a href="http://axis.apache.org/axis2/java/core/" target="_blank">Apache Axis 1 and 2</a></li>
                <li>WS Security with <a href="http://axis.apache.org/axis2/java/rampart/index.html" target="_blank">Apache Rampart</a> using configuration files as well as WS-Security Policy Language</li>
              </ul>
            <li>Languages: Java, C, PHP, SQL, Prolog, Cobol</li>
            <li>System Administration: Windows Server and GNU/Linux (Ubuntu, CentOS). Management of different services: DHCP,  Virtualization using VMware, network services, Open SSH, etc</li>
            <li>Other technologies: <a href="http://www.hibernate.org" target="_blank">Hibernate</a>, JDOM,</li>
            <li>Databases: <a href="http://www.mysql.com" target="_blank">MySQL</a>, HSQL, <a href="http://www.postgresql.org" target="_blank">Postgress</a></li>
          </ul>
        </td>
      </tr>   
    </table>

  </g:HTMLPanel>
  
  </g:ScrollPanel>
</ui:UiBinder> 